#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:3
msgid "Please wait..."
msgstr "Arhoswch os gwelwch yn dda..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:7
msgid "Computing the new partitions..."
msgstr "Yn cyfrifo'r rhaniadau newydd..."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:11
msgid ""
"This probably happened because the selected disk or free space is too small "
"to be automatically partitioned."
msgstr ""
"Mae'n debyg digwyddodd hyn oherwydd mae'r disg neu ofod rhydd a ddewiswyd yn "
"rhy fach i'w rhaniadu'n awtomatig."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:17
msgid "Failed to partition the selected disk"
msgstr "Methwyd rhaniadu'r disg a ddewiswyd"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:17
msgid ""
"This probably happened because there are too many (primary) partitions in "
"the partition table."
msgstr ""
"Mae'n debyg digwyddodd hyn oherwydd mae gormod o rhaniadau (cynradd) yn y "
"tabl rhaniadau."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:24
msgid "Partitioning method:"
msgstr "Dull rhaniadu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:24
msgid ""
"This installer can guide you through partitioning a disk for use by Debian, "
"or if you prefer, you can do it manually. If you do choose to use the guided "
"partitioning tool, you will still have a chance later to see the results, "
"customise it, and even undo the partitioning if you do not like it."
msgstr ""
"Gall y sefydlydd hwn eich arwain drwy rhaniadu disg er mwyn ei ddefnyddio "
"gyda Debian yn awtomatig, neu os hoffech, gallwch ei wneud e â llaw. Os "
"ydych chi'n dewis defnyddio'r teclyn rhaniadu arweiniedig, cewch gyfle yn "
"hwyrach i weld y canlyniadau, eu addasu nhw, a hyd yn oed datwneud y "
"rhaniadu os nad ydych chi'n ei hoffi."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:34
msgid "Disk space to partition:"
msgstr "Gofod disg i'w rhaniadu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:39
msgid "Partitioning scheme:"
msgstr "Cynllun rhaniadu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:39
msgid ""
"The disk can be partitioned using one of several different schemes. If you "
"are unsure, choose the first one."
msgstr ""
"Gellir rhaniadu'r disg gan ddefnyddio un o nifer o gynlluniau gwahanol. Os "
"nad ydych chi'n siwr, dewiswch yr un cyntaf."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:45
msgid "Unusable free space"
msgstr "Gofod rhydd ni ellir defnyddio"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:45
msgid ""
"Partitioning failed because the chosen free space may not be used. There are "
"probably too many (primary) partitions in the partition table."
msgstr ""
"Methodd rhaniadu oherwydd ni ellir defnyddio'r gofod rhydd a ddewiswyd. Mwy "
"na thebyg, mae gormod o rhaniadau (cynradd) yn y tabl rhaniadau."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:57
msgid "Guided partitioning"
msgstr "Rhaniadu arweiniedig"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:61
msgid "Use the largest continuous free space"
msgstr "Defnyddio'r gofod rhydd parhaol mwyaf"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. for example "Erase entire disk: IDE0 master - Maxtor 46L489"
#: ../partman-auto.templates:66
msgid "Erase entire disk: ${DEVICE}"
msgstr "Dileu'r disg cyfan: ${DEVICE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:70
msgid "Manually edit partition table"
msgstr "Golygu'r tabl rhaniadau â llaw"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:74
msgid "Automatically partition the free space"
msgstr "Rhaniadu'r gofod rhydd yn awtomatig"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:78
msgid "All files in one partition (recommended for new users)"
msgstr "Pob ffeil ar un rhaniad (argymhellir ar gyfer defnyddwyr newydd)"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:82
msgid "Separate partition for home directories"
msgstr "Rhaniad ar wahan ar gyfer cyfeiriaduron cartref"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../partman-auto.templates:86
msgid "Multi-user system"
msgstr "System aml-ddefnyddiwr"

